 9/2/16 . We are get into a busi track now ; 13 steamer pass outward today . We were past Aden at 5 P.M. and are well into the Red Sea this even . Aden is a bare sunsmitten place to look at . 10/2/16 . A chap die today , and they buri him this even with militari honour I saw a locust fall on the deck today and there was absolut no land in sight . 11/2/16 . Pay Day ! We pass a french mail steamer today . She was in sight at daylight but it took us all day to catch her . The Steward gave a good concert ; and the Colonel gave out the prize won in the sport competit . The ship 's captain , a veri decent old chap span a yarn or two also .
